AVEO The shorts are running away from AVEO Pharmaceuticals Inc AVEO stock The latest set of short interest data was released on 30 April 2019 and the numbers show a drop in short interest in AVEO shares While short interest still represents only 1393 of AVEOs float the number of shares shorted have fallen by 4463974 The number of shares shorted fell to 22322892 shares down from 26786866 shares during the preceding fortnight With average daily trading volumes at 3584000 shares days to cover increased to about 1238985 days The most recent news story about the stock that appeared in Yahoo Finances news section was titled Implied Volatility Surging for AVEO Pharmaceuticals AVEO Stock Options and dated May 22 2019
